Binary/source change: animated GIF support
=========================================

Purpose
-------
Add timer-driven animation support for GIF files loaded from the filesystem.
FreeImage exposes GIF frames through OpenMultiBitmap, so this patch decodes
GIF frames and their FrameTime metadata, then advances the displayed frame
from a wx.Timer attached to the canvas panel.

