Known caveats
-------------
Animated GIF support currently applies to normal filesystem GIFs. GIFs inside
archives still use the existing single-frame stream loader. Animated WebP still
loads as a still image because FreeImage 3.18 reports only one WebP multi-page
page for an animated WebP sample.

